   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give quality education to children in Piaui Brazil</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help us offer a better future to students of Piaui, Brazil. Support the Ayrton Senna Institute to ensure kids learn to read and write at a proper age. Brazil public schools lack resources to give children the quality education they deserve; It&apos;s our goal to reverse the &quot;age-grade gap&quot; phenomenon, cycle that begins when students become discouraged with their lack of progress in school, lose interest, fall behind and drop out, deciding a full-time job is more valuable than an education.</narrative>
  </description>
